                        <interp inst="t18360509-name-580" type="surname" value="HALL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360509-name-580" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH HALL</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Milford-wharf, Strand. On the 9th of May, about a quarter before three o'clock, I was passing along Thames-street, and felt a tug at my pocket—I turned round, and saw a boy about sixteen years old passing something to the prisoner—I ran after the prisoner, call<lb></lb>ing "Stop thief"—I overtook him, collared him, and took my handker<lb></lb>chief from under his coat—it has my name in full on it.</p>
