                  </hi>. I live in the City-road. I saw a young man pick the gentleman's pocket—the prisoner ran, snatched the handker<lb></lb>chief from the one who took it and walked away—I went after him, call<lb></lb>ing "Stop thief", he was putting it in coat—I stopped him, he said, he picked it up off the pavement.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi> I picked it off the pavement and gave it to the gentleman. <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi> He was going from the gentleman.</p>
